    <item>
      <title>纽约法官在封口费审判前扩大了特朗普的禁言令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/trump-gag-order-expanded-by-ny-judge-before-hush-money-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本月主持唐纳德·特朗普封口费审判的纽约法官扩大了该案的禁言令，此前这位前总统在社交媒体上攻击了法官和他的女儿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/trump-gag-order-expanded-by-ny-judge-before-hush-money-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 00:17:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普支付 1.75 亿美元债券以避免资产被扣押</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/donald-trump-posts-bond-to-freeze-454m-civil-fraud-fine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普兑现了他的承诺，将支付 1.75 亿美元的保释金，以在上诉期间搁置一项大规模民事欺诈判决，以确保纽约州不会开始扣押这位前总统的资产，至少目前不会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/donald-trump-posts-bond-to-freeze-454m-civil-fraud-fine</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 00:16:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜在韩国投票前发射弹道导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/north-korea-fires-ballistic-missile-ahead-of-south-s-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在韩国议会席位全国选举前几天，朝鲜发射了至少一枚疑似中程弹道导弹，以展示武力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/north-korea-fires-ballistic-missile-ahead-of-south-s-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 23:07:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列取消先前的访问后同意美国就拉法举行会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/israel-agrees-to-us-talks-on-rafah-after-scrapping-earlier-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡因关系日益恶化而取消了早些时候的访问后，美国和以色列同意举行面对面会议，讨论以色列预计入侵加沙地带南部城市拉法的争端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/israel-agrees-to-us-talks-on-rafah-after-scrapping-earlier-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 21:27:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登竞选团队在佛罗里达州堕胎投票措施中看到机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/biden-team-touts-abortion-access-as-florida-adds-ballot-measure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登竞选高级官员强调了民主党在 2024 年总统选举中对堕胎问题的重视，佛罗里达州法院周一批准了一项关于生殖权利的全州投票倡议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/biden-team-touts-abortion-access-as-florida-adds-ballot-measure</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 21:23:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最终医疗保险优惠率令人失望，健康保险公司股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/final-medicare-advantage-notice-shows-no-boost-from-initial-rate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国监管机构没有像业界预期的那样增加私人医疗保险计划的支付，健康保险股周一尾盘大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/final-medicare-advantage-notice-shows-no-boost-from-initial-rate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 20:32:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院议长约翰逊寻求妥协以加快对乌克兰的援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/us-speaker-johnson-searches-for-compromise-to-speed-ukraine-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议院议长迈克·约翰逊希望“立即”批准新的乌克兰援助，但仍在努力软化强硬派的反对，这让人怀疑数十亿美元的援助能否及时到达前线以发挥作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/us-speaker-johnson-searches-for-compromise-to-speed-ukraine-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 20:09:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>价值 15,000 美元的劳力士可能会降低秘鲁领导人 9% 的支持率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/why-a-scandal-over-a-rolex-watch-is-threatening-peru-s-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迪娜·博卢阿特（Dina Boluarte）发现了领导一个经常监禁前总统的国家的风险，因此建立了一座特殊监狱来关押他们。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/why-a-scandal-over-a-rolex-watch-is-threatening-peru-s-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 18:57:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷击败对冲基金因 GDP 挂钩认股权证提起的诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/argentina-defeats-hedge-fund-suits-over-gdp-linked-securities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷赢得了驳回 Aurelius Capital Management 和其他对冲基金的诉讼，这些诉讼要求支付与南美国家经济表现相关的证券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/argentina-defeats-hedge-fund-suits-over-gdp-linked-securities</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 18:22:57 GMT</pubDate>
